enjoy videos from your UPnP/DLNA media server or SMB share in the same Wi-Fi. A easy-to-set-up PC Client is available to support streaming from PC = Save your Storage! \nNo need to manually set the stereo mode such as 180\u00b0 or 3D side-by-side; SKYBOX would recognize the correct format for you = Save your Life! \n\nFeatures include: \n1. Automatically recognize video stereo mode ( 180\u00b0 / 360\u00b0 / 2D / 3D ). \n2. AirScreen: stream videos to multiple headsets (download here: https://SKYBOX.xyz/en/download/)\n3. Support DLNA media servers and SMB (1.0 & 2.0) shares. \n4. 5K local and streaming playback. \n5. Simple and intuitive UI; Spectacular VR environment. \n\nRelax and enjoy SKYBOX :)", "short_description": "SKYBOX is an ultimate local VR video player which supports video playback from local storage and network shared servers. \n\nWith SKYBOX, enjoy videos from your UPnP/DLNA media server or SMB share in the same Wi-Fi. A easy-to-set-up PC Client is available to support streaming from PC = Save your Storage! \n\nNo need to manually set the stereo mode such as 180\u00b0 or 3D side-by-side; SKYBOX would recognize the correct format for you = Save your Life!"}]}, "developer_name": "SKYBOX STUDIO", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://skybox.xyz/en/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://skybox.xyz/en/terms-of-use/", "publisher_name": "SKYBOX STUDIO", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://SKYBOX.XYZ/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "434961926215971"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["MOVIE", "MEDIA_PLAYER", "SOCIAL"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "zh_CN", "zh_HK